{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_08_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 2話 舌で味わうのも観光です",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃじゃーん！\nこちら、山形一になる予定の酒造『奥山酒造』です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da~!\nThis is Okuyama Shuzo‚ the sake brewery that’s going to be #1 in Yamagata!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "いずれ日本一にもなります！\n今からファンになっておくと、通ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’ll be number one in Japan someday too!\nIf you become a fan now‚ you’ll be ahead of the curve.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お、おぉ……\n山形一、そして日本一か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-oh…\nYamagata’s number one‚ and then Japan’s‚ huh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.976230554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.274308459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "って、うちの実家なんですけどね、えへへ……\nでも、いい場所なので見ていって下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s actually my family’s home‚ ehehe…\nBut please take a look around‚ it’s a nice place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3409751256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "この時間ならみんな、裏にいると思うので\nちょっと呼んできますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone should be in the back at this hour‚\nSo I’ll go call them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.474308459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　いや、仕事の邪魔になるんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? No‚ won’t that interrupt their work…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3076417923,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.3076417923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないですよ\n家族をご紹介したいので！　少しだけ待ってて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it won’t.\nI want to introduce you to my family! Just wait a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5704761823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.0038095157
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いやぁ……お兄さん、気合いが入ってたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… Your brother was really fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0371405602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ、まさか、兄妹で同じことを……\nちょっと恥ずかしいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I can’t believe we both said the same thing…\nThat’s a little embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4681220691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.6117662748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "山形一になる酒造です！\nいずれ日本一にもなりますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the sake brewery that’s going to be number one in Yamagata!\nIt’ll be number one in Japan someday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.4450543404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！\n真似しないでほしいっちゃ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nDon’t copy me~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2783914884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.27766517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、熱いものを感じたよ\n俺も負けていられないと身が引き締まった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I felt their passion.\nIt motivated me to not lose either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8992736816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それに、お母さんもお父さんも\n優しくて気さくな人達だったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And your mother and father…\nThey’re kind and friendly people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7548343976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.3714896203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、緊張しましたけど\n家族をご紹介出来て良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ I was nervous‚\nBut I’m glad I could introduce my family to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2048267683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、次は酒造の方をご紹介しますね！\nどうぞ奥へ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ let me show you the brewery!\nPlease come inside!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7172489877,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5695.166365199995,
          "startTime": 89.799995931
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.8715010644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "見て下さい！　うちで作ったお酒がズラリ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look! All of the sake we made is lined up here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.9381654423,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 92.7048343977
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.7714987756
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "冷蔵ケースで完成品の保存状態はバッチリ\nいつでも美味しく召し上がっていただけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The finished products are perfectly preserved in the refrigerated cases‚\nSo you can enjoy them at their best at any time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.9381677311,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.1381634077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "商品の温度管理がしっかりしているのは当然ですけど\nここは、水や気温が酒造りに適した土地でもあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It goes without saying that we strictly manage the temperature of our products‚\nBut this is also a ideal land for sake brewing in terms of water and temperature.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.3314715568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "ほんのちょっと田舎かもしれませんけど\nこだわりがあって、これがうちの味なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a little bit rural‚\nBut we have our own way of doing things‚ and this is our flavor.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1040353324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8381634077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ、という訳で\nそんな自慢の味を体験していただこうかと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So!\nI’d like you to experience this taste we’re so proud of!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0381656965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.1048300744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "こちら、利き酒セットをご用意しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here’s a sake tasting set!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.1048300744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.3048300744
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、この後一緒に観光大使の仕事に行くだろ？\n気持ちは嬉しいが、今は飲めないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we’re going to do the tourism ambassador job together later‚ right?\nI appreciate the thought‚ but I can’t drink right now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.599995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okuyamasake-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okuyamasake-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6242216748
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_08_02-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの実家の家業について理解を深める！\nというのも立派な仕事だと思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Deepening your understanding of an idol’s family business!\nI think that’s also a respectable job!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.899995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
