      "text": "じ、実家のことだからか、熱量が凄いな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… You're really passionate about it because it’s family’s business…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.0242216748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
